# Sample Usage Example

## Step 1: Create a Link
- Open Streamlit dashboard: `http://localhost:8501`  
- Go to **Create Link** tab  
- Enter a URL like:
```

[https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Software_engineering](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Software_engineering)

```
- Click **Shorten**
---

## Step 2: Generated Output
Example short URL:
```

[http://localhost:8000/1](http://localhost:8000/1)

```
---

## Step 3: Test the Redirect
- Copy the short URL  
- Open it in a new browser tab  
- You will be instantly redirected to the original page  

---

## Step 4: View Analytics
- Go to **View Analytics** tab  
- Enter short code (e.g., `1`)  
- Click **Get Stats**  

You will see:
- Click count graph  
- Timestamp data  
- IP address  
- Browser/User-Agent details  

